posting_body: Fantastic structure, ideal location, and roomy layout!
Views to the west from the living room, kitchen, balcony, and master bedroom.
Kitchen, dining, and living areas all have an open floor layout.
Finishes include travertine bathrooms and showers, bespoke window treatments, gas cooking, granite countertops, bar seating, and ALL appliances.
Amazing pool, barbecue grills, on-site fitness center, 24 hour concierge, stunning lobby, 5 minute walk to Lady Bird Lake, infinite retail and restaurants,
